import React from "react";
import {Box, Typography, styled, Button, Stack} from "@mui/material"
import Background from "./../Images/HeroBackground.jpg";

const RightBox = styled(Box)({
    backgroundImage:`url(${Background})`, 
    minHeight:"100vh",
    backgroundSize: "100% 100%",
});

const StyledBox = styled(Box)({
    background: "#BFD200",
    height: "60px",
    display: "flex",
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
});

export default function Hero() {
    return (
        <Box >
            <StyledBox>
                <Typography variant="h4">
                    DEIN DIGITALER 
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{fontWeight:"bold", p:"5px"}}>
                    CO-TRAINER
                </Typography>
            </StyledBox>
            <RightBox>
                <Box>
                    <Typography>
                        COACHING MADE EASY
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        MINIMALER AUFWAND.
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        MAXIMALER ERFOLG.
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        Weil der Trainerjob Spa√ü machen soll!
                    </Typography>
                    <Button>
                        LOS GEHT'S
                    </Button>
                </Box>
                <Stack>
                    <Stack>
                        <Typography>
                            6.000+
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            Trainer
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                    <Stack>
                        <Typography>
                            5 Mio
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            Trainings
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                    <Stack>
                        <Typography>
                            3.000+
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            Spiele
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                </Stack>
            </RightBox>
        </Box>
    )
}
